        <Parent_String>electromagnetic radiation [300056054], radiation (energy) [300379541], energy [300056007], energy and related concepts [300055211], physics concepts [300229371], physical sciences concepts [300065446], scientific concepts [300056006], Associated Concepts (hierarchy name) [300055126], Associated Concepts Facet [300264086]</Parent_String>
